results.title: Every Moment Matters - Cricut - Silhouette - Cameo - Instant Download Cut Files - SVG - PNG - JPG - Gif
results.description:
For hundreds more budget friendly, high quality cuttable images and designs click: https://www.etsy.com/shop/SaltySirenDesign?ref=seller-platform-mcnav
__________________________________________________

IF USING SVG FILES FOR A CUTTING MACHINE PLEASE READ:
Our files are large in size because a majority of our buyers use commercial sized machines in which the files must be larger and of higher quality. If you are using these files with a home use machine such as a Cricut when you first open them they might seem large and overhang your cutting area, files are very easily sized down using the resizing tool on the top right of the toolbar of Cricut Design Space and will cut beautifully on your machine at whatever size you wish to size them down to.

Please NOTE if Using a Cricut Machine a SVG File is a Vector image file type. These files are uploaded as previously designed by me and will automatically be separated into the design layers after uploading and saving your file to Cricut. In Cricut BEFORE CUTTING you ABSOLUTELY MUST click the "WELD" button at the bottom right hand side of the program, by doing this it will ensure a smooth cut of your graphics. Most people who are familiar with the Cricut Design Space are familiar with how to WELD but if you are new to the program and have any questions please send me a message and I will be happy to walk you through it.

If you have any questions at all or any problems whatsoever with any of our files or downloading them please contact us directly and we will get back to you as quickly as we can within 12 hours. We fully stand by our work and our product so if you are unhappy, we are unhappy and will do everything in our power to make it right.

Here is a link that is helpful as well if you are new to Cricut: https://help.cricut.com/hc/en-us/articles/360009556313-Uploading-Images-into-Design-Space

Image Sized  1500 X 1500 Pixels - 300 DPI
You will receive 4 download files with your purchase
-SVG
-JPG
-PNG
-GIF

Files can be used to print and put on clothing or cut with a Cricut, Silhouette Printer, laser engraver. Please note that files with smaller intricate details will come across better printed verses cut, if looking to cut your files for stickers or decals choose designs with more bold prints and thicker designs. 

All purchases and downloads are final sale; however we thrive to offer the best customer service possible and are happy to help in whatever way we can, so if you have any issues at all with a file please contact us so that we can resolve your issue for you. 

Downloads are available immediately upon purchase as soon as Etsy processes your payment. To access your downloads go to your purchases tab and the downloads will be available for you to save to your computer and start creating.

All purchases come with a design release download so that you can use the files for your small business sales. You may place our designs on any products of the tangible form that you wish to re-sell. The commercial design release allows you to place the designs on an unlimited amount of product as long as it is a tangible, non digital product. Examples are t-shirts, dish towels, canvas bags, mugs, tumblers, bumper stickers, key chains, posters, wall hangings, ect... ANYTHING THAT IS TANGIBLE is fine to re-sell in your business or shop. 

We DO NOT authorize the re-sale of our designs in the digital form. This means no re-selling our designs as a download and no up-loading our designs to the internet for digital distribution. 

All images come with watermark logo removed.

results.title: 20oz Tumbler saying Live, Laugh and Love on a dazzling background of Tie Dye colors.  Great gift for Mother's Day or Birthday
results.description:
Vivid pink, blue, purple and green.  20oz tumbler with a saying "Live - every moment, Laugh - every day, and Love - beyond words".  The colors are sublimated and very clear.  The image surrounds the entire cup.  The cup is brilliant with the Tie Dye background and black print.  The metal tumbler has been sublimated and the design surrounds the tumbler.  It has a way of making you feel like your living back in the days of the Flower Child.  It is very Boho.  I am able to customize this cup if you would like to put a name on the front or back.  Would make a beautiful gift for a best friend, mother's day, somebody you know is retiring, birthday or just because.  We often buy gifts for friends and acquaintances and we don't know have a clue of what to give them. This is the perfect gift.  Anybody that is ready for a nice summer day would love this tumbler. I offer free shipping and quick turnaround.  

Thank you,

Jennie Heskin-Mills
MillsiesDesigns
heskin@aol.com
